                         "erasHtml":  "\u003cdiv class=\"discography\"\u003e\n                \u003cdiv class=\"album\"\u003e\n                  \u003cstrong\u003eEarly Soulful Rise\u003c/strong\u003e\n                  \u003cspan\u003eThe opening stage where Donell Jones developed a reputation for polished, emotional songwriting.\u003c/span\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n                \u003cdiv class=\"album\"\u003e\n                  \u003cstrong\u003eClassic R\u0026amp;B Peak\u003c/strong\u003e\n                  \u003cspan\u003eThe era where his biggest songs made him a defining voice of romantic urban music.\u003c/span\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n                \u003cdiv class=\"album\"\u003e\n                  \u003cstrong\u003eEnduring Quiet Legacy\u003c/strong\u003e\n                  \u003cspan\u003eA later chapter defined by respect, replay value, and timeless emotional connection.\u003c/span\u003e\n                \u003c/div\u003e\n              \u003c/div\u003e",
